snippet: Just hours before a 72-hour cease-fire was set to expire early Friday, two rockets fired from Gaza hit southern Israel, the Israel Defense Forces said.
abstract: Israeli military says just hours before 72-hour cease-fire with Hamas was set to expire, two rockets fired from Gaza hit southern Israel.
lead_paragraph: Just hours before a 72-hour cease-fire was set to expire early Friday, two rockets fired from Gaza hit southern Israel, the Israel Defense Forces said.
